						<p>Slab at the foot of the hill.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">9th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>It states that Ayyapa son of Kaṇṇabbe made a grant of 225 house sites each measuring 9 hands in with and 50 hands in length to the city named Ayyaṇa-Śrīpura. It is in characters of 9th century A.D.</p>						

